title: Marriage of Cupid and Psyche
description: Set of scenic wallpaper "Les Amours de Psyche", consisting of 26 panels which form 12 scenes based on the Jean de la Fontiane story  "Les Amours de Psyche" (1669). Scene depicts the marriage of Cupid and Psyche.
